(174, 'Refrigerate', 'O golpes de Type Normal serão transformados em Ice, além de seu dano aumentar.'),
(175, 'Sweet Veil', 'Prevents itself and its allies from falling asleep.'),
(176, 'Stance Change', 'The Pokémon changes form depending on how it battles.'),
(177, 'Gale Wings', 'Gives priority to Flying-type moves.'),
(178, 'Mega Launcher', 'Se o Pokémon com esta habilidade usar um golpe que for baseado em aura ou pulso o Ataque do golpe irá aumentar em 50%.'),
(179, 'Grass Pelt', 'Boosts the Defense stat in Grassy Terrain.'),
(180, 'Symbiosis', 'The Pokémon can pass an item to an ally.'),
(181, 'Tough Claws', 'Se o Pokémon com esta habilidade usar um golpe que faça contato com o Pokémon inimigo o Ataque do golpe irá aumentar em 30%.'),
(182, 'Pixilate', 'O golpes de Type Normal serão transformados em Fairy, além de seu dano aumentar.'),
(183, 'Gooey', 'Contact with the Pokémon lowers the attackers Speed stat.'),
(184, 'Aerilate', 'O golpes de Type Normal serão transformados em Flying, além de seu dano aumentar.'),
(185, 'Parental Bond', 'O Pokémon com esta habilidade pode atacar juntamente com seu filho, dando assim, 25% de chance de ataque duplo.'),
(186, 'Dark Aura', 'Se o Pokémon com esta habilidade entrar em batalha e o Pokémon oponente não tiver Aura Break, todos os golpes Type Dark irão aumentar o dano.'),
(187, 'Fairy Aura', 'Se o Pokémon com esta habilidade entrar em batalha e o Pokémon oponente não tiver Aura Break, todos os golpes Type Fairy irão aumentar o dano.'),
(188, 'Aura Break', 'Se o Pokémon com está habilidade estiver em batalha os golpes do Type Dark/Fairy terão dano reduzido.'),
(189, 'Primordial Sea', 'Causes heavy rain.'),
(190, 'Desolate Land', 'Creates harsh sunlight.'),
(191, 'Delta Stream', 'Eliminates weather effects and eliminates weaknesses of Flying-type Pokémon.'),
(192, 'Stamina', 'Boosts the Defense stat when hit by an attack.'),
(193, 'Wimp Out', 'The Pokémon cowardly switches out when its HP becomes half or less.'),
(194, 'Emergency Exit', 'The Pokémon, sensing danger, switches out when its HP becomes half or less.'),
(195, 'Water Compaction', 'Boosts the Pokémons Defense stat sharply when hit by a Water-type move.'),
(196, 'Merciless', 'The Pokémons attacks become critical hits if the target is poisoned.'),
(197, 'Shields Down', 'When its HP becomes half or less, the Pokémons shell breaks and it becomes aggressive.'),
(198, 'Stakeout', 'Doubles the damage dealt to the targets replacement if the target switches out.'),
(199, 'Water Bubble', 'Se o Pokémon com esta habilidade usar um golpe Type Water o Ataque irá aumentar em 50%, como também reduz em 50% o dano de golpes do Type Fire que ele for atacado.'),
(200, 'Steelworker', 'Se o Pokémon atacante usar um golpe Type Steel, o Ataque do golpe irá dobrar.'),
(201, 'Berserk', 'Boosts the Pokémons Sp. Atk stat when it takes a hit that causes its HP to become half or less.'),
(202, 'Slush Rush', 'Boosts the Pokémons Speed stat in a hailstorm.'),
(203, 'Long Reach', 'The Pokémon uses its moves without making contact with the target.'),
(204, 'Liquid Voice', 'Se o Pokémon com esta habilidade usar um golpe que for baseado em som, o golpe se transformará em Type Water.'),
(205, 'Triage', 'Gives priority to a healing move.'),
(206, 'Galvanize', 'O golpes de Type Normal serão transformados em Electric, além de seu dano aumentar.'),
(207, 'Surge Surfer', 'Doubles the Pokémons Speed stat on Electric Terrain.'),
(208, 'Schooling', 'When it has a lot of HP, the Pokémon forms a powerful school. It stops schooling when its HP is low.'),
(209, 'Disguise', 'O Pokémon com esta habilidade tem a possibilidade de se disfarçar algumas vezes aleatoriamente, sendo assim ele não tomara dano do golpe caso esteja disfarçado.'),
(210, 'Battle Bond', 'Defeating an opposing Pokémon strengthens the Pokémons bond with its Trainer, and it becomes Ash-Greninja. Water Shuriken gets more powerful.'),
(211, 'Power Construct', 'Other Cells gather to aid when its HP becomes half or less. Then the Pokémon changes its form to Complete Forme.'),
(212, 'Corrosion', 'The Pokémon can poison the target even if its a Steel or Poison type.'),
(213, 'Comatose', 'Its always drowsing and will never wake up. It can attack without waking up.'),
(214, 'Queenly Majesty', 'Its majesty pressures the opposing Pokémon, making it unable to attack using priority moves.'),
(215, 'Innards Out', 'Damages the attacker landing the finishing hit by the amount equal to its last HP.'),
(216, 'Dancer', 'When another Pokémon uses a dance move, it can use a dance move following it regardless of its Speed.'),
(217, 'Battery', 'Powers up ally Pokémons special moves.'),
(218, 'Fluffy', 'Halves the damage taken from moves that make direct contact, but doubles that of Fire-type moves.'),
(219, 'Dazzling', 'Surprises the opposing Pokémon, making it unable to attack using priority moves.'),
(220, 'Soul-Heart', 'Boosts its Sp. Atk stat every time a Pokémon faints.'),
(221, 'Tangling Hair', 'Contact with the Pokémon lowers the attackers Speed stat.'),
(222, 'Receiver', 'The Pokémon copies the Ability of a defeated ally.'),
(223, 'Power of Alchemy', 'The Pokémon copies the Ability of a defeated ally.'),
(224, 'Beast Boost', 'The Pokémon boosts its most proficient stat each time it knocks out a Pokémon.'),
(225, 'RKS System', 'Changes the Pokémon’s type to match the memory disc it holds.'),
(226, 'Electric Surge', 'Turns the ground into Electric Terrain when the Pokémon enters a battle.'),
(227, 'Psychic Surge', 'Turns the ground into Psychic Terrain when the Pokémon enters a battle.'),
(228, 'Misty Surge', 'Turns the ground into Misty Terrain when the Pokémon enters a battle.'),
(229, 'Grassy Surge', 'Turns the ground into Grassy Terrain when the Pokémon enters a battle.'),
(230, 'Full Metal Body', 'Prevents other Pokémons moves or Abilities from lowering the Pokémons stats.'),
(231, 'Shadow Shield', 'Se o Pokémon com esta habilidade tiver com HP FULL o dano dos golpes que receber será reduzido pela metade.'),
(232, 'Prism Armor', 'Reduz o dano de golpes super-efetivos (2x ou 4x) que ele sofrer em 25%.'),
(233, 'Neuroforce', 'Aumentará em 25% o dano de golpe super-efetivos (2x ou 4x) do Pokémon atacante.');
